\details{
Let \eqn{\mathcal{P}} denote the set of planning units, \eqn{\mathcal{A}} the
set of actions, and \eqn{\mathcal{F}} the set of features.

Let \eqn{x_{ia} \in \{0,1\}} denote whether action \eqn{a \in \mathcal{A}} is
