A target for feature \eqn{f} is stored as an absolute threshold
\eqn{T_f \ge 0}, together with metadata describing how that threshold was
defined. When the optimization model is built, the target is translated into a
constraint of the form
\deqn{
\sum_{(i,a) \in \mathcal{S}_f} c_{iaf} x_{ia} \ge T_f,
